vote.title: An ordinance granting renewal of a revocable license to 7-Eleven, Inc., for the use of a total of approximately 60 square feet of aerial space to occupy, maintain and utilize two blade signs, a facade sign, and a canopy without a premise sign on portions of Field and Commerce Streets rights-of-way near its intersection with Main Street - Revenue: General Fund $3,000.00 annually, plus the $100.00 one-time fee and $20.00 ordinance publication fee
